project.name: Platform Game
project.notes: The hero (aka the watermelon) starts with 10 lives. If the hero falls into the lava pit of scene 1 or touches the enemy of scene 2 he loses a life. Should the enemy be a knife? Or salt? :P His goal is to end up in the watermelon bowl. Movement: If touching left edge and trying to go left, you cant. If touching right edge then switch to 2nd, 3rd screens. If jump, make sure no bugs about jumping.
